
Ranger Help for: followers
==========================

SUMMARY:    
Once a Ranger is trusted enough by Nature, he or she may be able to call
a follower to their side. The race of follower a Ranger will get, will
depend on the Ranger's primary terrain. It could be anything from a worm
to an elephant. Some followers are smarter than others, and can be trained
to perform special tasks that can benefit the Ranger. Keep in mind though,
every time a Ranger allows his or her follower to die, the stinch of death
will stick to the Ranger and future followers may refuse to come to his or
her aid forever. Your follower's race will never be the same as your enemy
species.

=============================================================================
